Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,(让人妻职员成为性奴隶\N全员持续轮奸研修旅行)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我轮奸过人妻三次\N非常喜欢做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,人妻被男人围着痛苦的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一想到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就勃起了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅如此 人妻都是有老公的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,人妻对她们的老公来说是宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我践踏太太的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,让她老公使用的小穴\N共享给大家使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这样被践踏的太太\N是多麽色情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她对老公感到羞愧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,脸变得红透 拚命做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,抽插她的胯部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,让她感觉到被男人\N围着的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.53,0:01:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,然後四面的精液乱射给她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,被放弃的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是用过後扔掉一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到後又勃起了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,继续射精给太太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很色魔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:02:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,给你介绍如此淫魔的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我的社长 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面 我叫友香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,把履历给我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,上个月失业了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为什麽辞职了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也算不上辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因为公司倒闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是不幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,工作内容很有价值吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是跟老公一起经营的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以一直在拚命工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我很理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,友香现在的情况很困难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我要找到工作才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正好有人辞职了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,现在人才不足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你会经营的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我会使用办公软体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,从事经营的人我很放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什麽疑问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我会努力工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没有其他疑问了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 面试就到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,过後我会联系你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一个美女来我公司面试
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是个结婚过的好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的色魔灵魂无法压抑住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,於是对她恶作剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看了我的胯部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,她无动於衷的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的女人对我来说是挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我录用她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(一个月後)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这个收据也许不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为什麽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,上个月的没有通过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,会被税务局的人骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,检查真严格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,立花 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,关於昨天给我的结算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这个数字我没有输入过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,确实错了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那就修正这里 然後复印
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,友香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有事情拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,关於下个月的研习旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,内容全部写在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,地点还有车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都写在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以负责一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有不懂的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我会联系预约的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,日程这样没有问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,友香看了我的胯部什麽\N反应也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我对她的反应非常兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法压抑到只能自慰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,然後又有了更兴奋的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,大家手上都有酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,友香 这周利润多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,两百八十万
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为五十万就很困难了\N这都是多亏大家的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,达到了五倍以上的营业额
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,社长好厉害哦\N都是多亏了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,乾杯\N乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去研修旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好好准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,多喝点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,多喝点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喝5杯也没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,眼前的景象让我感到很震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在我眼里她就像是\N被大家围着做爱一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,(研修旅行的当天)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天对我来说\N一辈子无法忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个适合旅行的天气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,带齐东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教\N上车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,大家帮拿一些行李\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大家要系好安全带\N接下来是长途开车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,需要上厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大家没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,友香 带了晕车药吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有带\N那我给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,想要哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那就出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,芦田没问题吧\N没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大家开心的去玩吧\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,社长也要开心点\N你被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,认真点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,总是这麽热闹吗\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,工作时候就认真\N玩的时候也要开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都这麽觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,第1次参加这种旅行\N有点紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,悠闲一些就可以了\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,友田能喝酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,酒量不好 但是我喜欢喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,酒量很弱吗 喝醉会怎麽样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,会生病的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喝酒要开心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,带了很多日本酒来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,日本酒很香的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我也喝不多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很好喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:13:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好宽敞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,承蒙你的照顾\N失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎大家今天到来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们旅馆已经经营60多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这个建筑很有历史
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大家可以好好参观
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,晚饭在7点准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我们精心准备的\N请大家好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,浴室在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有男女浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,非常方便 大家可以慢慢享用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请大家开心玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你们女性只有一位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,请好好玩耍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什麽其他问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,也许还要增加一些酒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这样喔\N好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麽事情就联系我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好好休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大家就住这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,友田住隔壁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,山田君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,日程就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我们去观光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,回到旅馆後就是饮酒会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,关於第2天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,发表一下自己的研修成果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会讨论整整一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,然後第3天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,第3天观光之後品嚐美食
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,然後就回去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大家知道了吗\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大家开心的度过这三天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好好学习
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我去观光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来喂他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我就只会这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这个年纪合适演这个角色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个好想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来猜拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,输掉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就要做害羞的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要唱歌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要这样子唱才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,输掉了就要唱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,歌词大意 把小穴张开\N把手插入好湿好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,再继续张开把肉棒插入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴高潮高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮的意思懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们经常玩的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谁输谁就要受到惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那就来猜拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来猜拳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,猜拳大会开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:19:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要惩罚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麽又输了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,输了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的好笨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,才喝一点就要去小便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他输了也没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不要管他了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,又输掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,再喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好的来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,没有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:22:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你弄错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.03,0:22:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没有弄错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你也要认真做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这样没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.05,0:22:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在说什麽奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什麽都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿这个回去哦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什麽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.29,0:22:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.82,0:22:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜拳太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我要进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.14,0:23:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.67,0:23:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,满分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你蹲下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快点唱歌跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,来唱歌跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.24,0:24:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.08,0:24:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要认真做
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.47,0:24:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样子回东京吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.79,0:24:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.08,0:24:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样对友田不好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.23,0:24:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.12,0:24:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.88,0:24:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.82,0:24:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.86,0:24:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.38,0:24:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.17,0:25:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.31,0:25:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.66,0:25:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.31,0:25:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是惩罚游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.42,0:25:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,必须要遵守哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.84,0:25:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,友田 友田
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.14,0:25:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉 脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.23,0:25:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是连衣裙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.61,0:25:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.79,0:25:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.02,0:25:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好性感
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.81,0:25:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.39,0:26:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,终於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.34,0:26:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是麦克风
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.98,0:26:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,自己拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.85,0:26:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着麦克风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.65,0:26:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快点唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.42,0:26:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,快点唱歌吧\N好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.75,0:26:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没有必要害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.60,0:26:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大家拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.33,0:27:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,让我听到声音
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.04,0:27:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.52,0:27:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,最後的声音没有听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.05,0:27:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.79,0:27:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.18,0:27:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,继续玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.40,0:27:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.68,0:27:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,讲好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.15,0:27:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好好站着
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.26,0:28:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,大家开心一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.83,0:28:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,把小穴张开
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.01,0:28:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.94,0:28:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.29,0:28:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,最後没有说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.38,0:28:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.80,0:28:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.14,0:28:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.65,0:28:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.76,0:28:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴变得很湿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.75,0:29:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.93,0:29:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.95,0:29:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,两次和三次都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.64,0:29:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.18,0:29:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.87,0:29:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,干什麽\N握着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.12,0:29:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,变成这样了\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.18,0:29:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.11,0:29:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴很湿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.66,0:29:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.06,0:30:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.71,0:30:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你太色情了 所以我好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.38,0:30:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很想做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.77,0:30:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,社长快收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.91,0:30:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.94,0:30:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.21,0:30:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,社长 这是不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.94,0:30:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.68,0:30:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.39,0:30:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,已经变得很湿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.86,0:30:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,很湿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.03,0:30:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这里好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.08,0:30:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.90,0:30:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这里好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.80,0:30:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.27,0:30:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.92,0:31:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.31,0:31:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.96,0:31:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.29,0:31:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.60,0:31:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.21,0:31:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.34,0:31:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
